overview: Following the story of young Toby (Jack Bailey), who is “A Virgin No More” after paying an overnight visit to his dad’s best friend ‘Uncle’ Carl (Dale Savage), and a devious instigator for setting up unsuspecting friend Will (Scott Finn) with the older man to curry favor in “The Offering,” Toby is now looking to settle a score with the help of his roommate (Trevor Harris).
title: A Virgin No More: Retaliation
